#Sound visualizer program

## 開発環境とプラットフォーム / Developping environment and platform
* [platformio](https://platformio.org/) 及び [Arduion](https://www.arduino.cc/) 環境にて開発 / [platformio](https://platformio.org/) with [Arduion](https://www.arduino.cc/) environemnt
* プログラムは当初Arduino Unoでテストし、その後BLE Nano V2およびTrinket M0に移植 / The program was first written for Arduino Uno, then modified for Redbear Lab's BLE nano v2, and Adafruit's Trinekt M0

